OL,3,CScottish Conservative peer defects to
OL,4,CReform UK
OL,6,FFormer Conservative life peer Malcolm
OL,7,FOfford has defected to Reform UK.
OL,9,FLord Malcolm Offord was announced by
OL,10,FNigel Farage as the latest defector to
OL,11,Fjoin the party during a rally in
OL,12,FFalkirk.
OL,14,FThe Scottish financier previously
OL,15,Fserved as a Scotland Office minister
OL,16,Fduring the last Conservative
OL,17,Fgovernment, and was the Scottish
OL,18,FTories' treasurer at the time of his
OL,19,Fdefection.
