OL,3,CScottish Conservative peer defects to
OL,4,CReform UK
OL,6,F"Today I can announce that I am
OL,7,Fresigning from the Conservative Party.
OL,8,FToday I am joining Reform UK and today
OL,9,FI announce my intention to stand for
OL,10,FReform in the Holyrood election in May
OL,11,Fnext year.
OL,13,F"That means that from today, for the
OL,14,Fnext five months, day and night, I
OL,15,Fshall be campaigning with all of you
OL,16,Ftirelessly for two objectives.
