OL,3,CScottish Conservative peer defects to
OL,4,CReform UK
OL,6,F"The first objective is to remove this
OL,7,Frotten SNP Government after 18 years,
OL,8,Fand the second is to present a
OL,9,Fpositive vision for Scotland inside
OL,10,Fthe UK, to restore Scotland to being a
OL,11,Fprosperous, proud, healthy and happy
OL,12,Fcountry."
OL,14,FThe Greenock-born businessman was made
OL,15,Fa life peer in 2021 by then prime
OL,16,Fminister Boris Johnson and served as a
OL,17,Fminister of exports from 2023 until
OL,18,Fthe general election in July 2024.
OL,20,FHe had previously donated nearly
OL,21,F#150,000 to the party.
