OL,3,CScottish Conservative peer defects to
OL,4,CReform UK
OL,6,FFollowing his peerage, he was made
OL,7,FBaron Offord of Garvel.
OL,9,FHe becomes Reform's latest high-
OL,10,Fprofile defection in Scotland.
OL,12,FThe party previously announced the
OL,13,Fdefection of Scottish Tory MSP Graham
OL,14,FSimpson, who also gave a speech at the
OL,15,FFalkirk rally, as well as a host of
OL,16,Fcouncillors around the country.
OL,18,FLord Offord criticised his old for
OL,19,Fparty for having "given up on
OL,20,FScotland".
