OL,6,FDuring his speech to Reform members at
OL,7,Fthe Macdonald Inchyra Hotel, Farage
OL,8,Frepeated claims that one in three
OL,9,Fschoolchildren in Glasgow do not speak
OL,10,FEnglish as their first language.
OL,12,FAsked about the comments by reporters,
OL,13,FLord Offord said: "I think he's
OL,14,Fhighlighting an issue which needs to
OL,15,Fbe talked about."
OL,17,FAsked if the comments represent a "dog
OL,18,Fwhistle", he continued: "I don't
OL,19,Fbelieve it's a dog whistle, I think
OL,20,Fit's a fact."
